text: Louis Dupré (with variant spellings) may refer to: * Louis Dupré (painter) (1789–1837), French painter * Louis Dupré (dancer) (1690–1774), French balletmaster and dancer * Louis Dupré (philosopher) (born 1925), Belgian- American philosopher * L. G. Dupre (1932–2001), American football player * Louis Dupree (professor) (1925–1989), American archaeologist
